item.title: RING POP PROGRAMMING!!!!!
item.author: nick@nick64.me (Nick64)
item.description: RING POP GAMING!!!! For real though, no more weird posts for a sec. Sorry for not saying a lot recently, I’ve been busy with school and work and… life, in general.
